{"_path":"/prestations/podologie-du-sport","_dir":"prestations","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Podologie du sport","description":"La podologie du sport est une spécialité car il faut connaitre le sport pour savoir quelles sont les contraintes que va rencontrer le sportif et apporter les meilleurs conseils aux sportifs.","image":{"src":"/job-podologie.jpg"},"date":"2024-08-05T00:00:00.000Z","badge":{"label":"Podologie"},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dans sa pratique sportive de loisir ou en compétition le sportif met à rude épreuve son organisme, il lui fait subir des contraintes mécaniques qui peuvent entrainer des pathologies à tout niveau : muscle, tendon, ligament, articulation, os."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Les pathologies les plus fréquentes sont :"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"La myoaponévrosite plantaire"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"La périostite tibiale"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Le syndrome de l’essuie-glace"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"La tendinite du tibial postérieur ou antérieur"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Le syndrome fémoro patellaire"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Les problèmes de dos"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Les tendinites"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Après un examen complet, si c’est nécessaire, on pourra réaliser des semelles orthopédiques thermoformées et prodiguer des conseils de chaussures, la chaussure est très importante dans la pratique sportive, orienter vers d’autres thérapeutes, pour bien prendre le sportif dans sa globalité et l’aider dans sa performance."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{"className":["flex","space-x-4","items-center","justify-between"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"femme saut","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/podologie_sport_1.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"homme running","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/podologie_sport_2.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"div","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"joggeur home","className":["rounded-lg"],"height":400,"src":"/podologie_sport_3.jpg","width":400},"children":[]}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:1.prestations:4.podologie-du-sport.md","_source":"content","_file":"1.prestations/4.podologie-du-sport.md","_stem":"1.prestations/4.podologie-du-sport","_extension":"md"}